## git status 命令；
## 创建一个readme.txt内容为Git is a version control system.Git is free software.添加进仓库；
## 修改第一行内容，改为Git is a distributed version control system.

$ git status
On branch master
Changes not staged for commit:
  (use "git add <file>..." to update what will be committed)
  (use "git checkout -- <file>..." to discard changes in working directory)

        modified:   readme

no changes added to commit (use "git add" and/or "git commit -a")

## status 命令是查看仓库当前状态，上面这段话说明了文件readme被修改过，但这个修改还没有被提交

## git diff 命令；
## 这个命令是查看文件到底修改了什么内容；

$ git diff
diff --git a/readme b/readme
index d8036c1..013b5bc 100644
--- a/readme
+++ b/readme
@@ -1,2 +1,2 @@
-Git is a version control system.
+Git is a distributed version control system.
 Git is free software.
\ No newline at end of file

## “-”号所指的是以前的版本，“+”号所指的是当前版本，没有标识符号就是没有改动；
## git add 提交这个修改；在 git commit 之前还可以git status再次查看仓库当前状态；在git commit之后也可以git status再次查看；

xh@DESKTOP-HO0HI6U MINGW64 ~/Desktop/learngit (master)
$ git add readme

xh@DESKTOP-HO0HI6U MINGW64 ~/Desktop/learngit (master)
$ git status
On branch master
Changes to be committed:
  (use "git reset HEAD <file>..." to unstage)

        modified:   readme


xh@DESKTOP-HO0HI6U MINGW64 ~/Desktop/learngit (master)
$ git commit -m"add a word"
[master 5d4cbad] add a word
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

xh@DESKTOP-HO0HI6U MINGW64 ~/Desktop/learngit (master)
$ git status
On branch master
nothing to commit, working tree clean

## 第一个git status说明了即将被提交的文件是readme；第二个git status说明了没有需要提交的修改，整个工作是干净的；

## 运用git status命令可以随时查看仓库状态，发现有修改，可以通过git diff来查看修改了那些内容。
